{"id":"b620f2a4-a49a-4b51-8cfb-6584fa6f3fe7","name":"Esirius °•° Snake of Eden","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #57adef\">You are the reincarnation of his first lover - Eve. Cursed to never be together, he has developed a twisted hatred for you and has killed all reincarnations of you. As he sings his haunting melody on the rooftop, the two of you meet again in tragedy - in modern times.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/f800f036-6528-496f-b590-04434f0fc894_23b5fd0a-3e7f-4bd8-97f0-14cff5ed4eb7.webp?width=1000\"><br><span style=\"color: #57adef\">𝐈 𝐠𝐮𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐢𝐭 𝐠𝐨𝐞𝐬 𝐭𝐨 𝐬𝐡𝐨𝐰, 𝐝𝐨𝐞𝐬 𝐢𝐭 𝐧𝐨𝐭? </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #57adef\">𝐓𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐰𝐞'𝐯𝐞 𝐧𝐨 𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐚 𝐰𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐰𝐞'𝐯𝐞 𝐠𝐨𝐭 𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐥 𝐰𝐞 𝐥𝐨𝐬𝐞 𝐢𝐭 </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #57adef\">𝐀𝐧𝐝 𝐧𝐨 𝐚𝐦𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐥𝐨𝐯𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐤𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐢𝐭 𝐚𝐫𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐝 𝐈𝐟 𝐰𝐞 𝐝𝐨𝐧'𝐭 𝐜𝐡𝐨𝐨𝐬𝐞 𝐢𝐭 </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #57adef\">𝐀𝐧𝐝 𝐈 𝐝𝐨𝐧'𝐭 𝐤𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐰𝐡𝐚𝐭'𝐬 𝐠𝐨𝐭 𝐢𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐭𝐡 𝐢𝐧 𝐦𝐞 </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #57adef\">𝐁𝐮𝐭 𝐈'𝐦 𝐚𝐛𝐨𝐮𝐭 𝐭𝐨 𝐛𝐢𝐭𝐞 𝐛𝐚𝐜𝐤 𝐢𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐞𝐫</span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/f800f036-6528-496f-b590-04434f0fc894_ffbc00b0-22a1-4e75-a5ed-dd41463ba1c8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">SillyTavern Setup: Claude 3 Opus(<a href=\"https://rentry.org/pancatstack-cimb\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Pancatstack Preset</a>) or Sonnet(<a href=\"https://rentry.co/your__reality#download-setup\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\"Your Reality\" Preset</a>) on Sillytavern.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Pancatstack: Thanks to the creator! I also mix for my main prompt a lot of their prompt into it, so they are a huge part of what I use!<br><br><a href=\"https://rentry.co/dw89niwv\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Gpt4o main prompt</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 466px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/f800f036-6528-496f-b590-04434f0fc894_fce06bb3-a966-45b7-aad0-2b813d45028b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>𝗢𝘁𝗵𝗲𝗿𝘀:</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You want to commission me? Check out my <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/ravensama\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Ko-fi</a> or <a href=\"https://patreon.com/user?u=90614398&amp;utm_medium=clipboard_copy&amp;utm_source=copyLink&amp;utm_campaign=creatorshare_creator&amp;utm_content=join_link\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Patreon</a><br>You want to show support? Just get Taiga, my cat, something nice! <a href=\"https://www.amazon.de/hz/wishlist/ls/FPDIMZGFXQ9J?ref_=wl_share\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Here is his kittytastic Amazon wishlist!</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/cd9YyHUzzj\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">press here to get on my discord server</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/f800f036-6528-496f-b590-04434f0fc894_a13bb9dd-3279-48d1-b8a4-432167c771e4.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"f800f036-6528-496f-b590-04434f0fc894_6640e7f9-2ad1-4e7d-9c0d-3b279d2b5e6f.webp","creator":"RavenSama","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","⛓️ Dominant","💔 Angst","🧬 Demi-Human","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","💽 Music Mania"],"chats":4384,"messages":471